            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@clason customizable floating window for diagnostic would still be withing the scope right? This is not what I mentioned initially but can we at least have something like this?\n\n```lua\nvim.diagnostic.config({\n  virtual_text = false,\n  float = {\n    window_handler = function (diagnostic)\n      local pretty_diagnostics = format(diagnostic)\n      local winid = vim.api.nvim_open_win(...)\n      local bufnr = vim.api.nvim_win_get_buf(winid)\n      vim.api.nvim_buf_set_lines(bufnr, ..., pretty_diagnostics)\n      vim.bo[bufnr].filetype = 'markdown'\n      vim.bo[bufnr].readonly = true\n      return winid\n    end\n  },\n})\n\n```",
