        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Correct me if I'm wrong, but LSP diagnostics cannot be Markdown according to the specification (which we take as gospel)?\n\nI added support for this in version 3.18 of the LSP: https://github.com/microsoft/language-server-protocol/pull/1905, and the PR to support this in Neovim is https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27693.\n\n@s1n7ax feel free to continue the work there!\n\n",
